{"tid":2054132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人患甲狀腺亢進","createTime":"2020-06-07T02:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T14:59:21.000Z","uid":59953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bb0aa32c143aeaf95bb18e68efa4235db7aae450","tid":2054132,"uid":59953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T02:22:05.000Z","msg":"每隔兩三年就復發<br />\n好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n有冇人根治到"},{"pid":"a92a5651a7713b53818e7ab6f329e782749d6d22","tid":2054132,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T02:26:08.000Z","msg":"有咩症狀？"},{"pid":"473031f26af9bcb01364454c223439b26f54f088","tid":2054132,"uid":59953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a92a5651a7713b53818e7ab6f329e782749d6d22","tid":2054132,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T02:26:08.000Z","msg":"有咩症狀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T02:39:08.000Z","msg":"心跳快 手震 失眠"},{"pid":"d7ce6410e91030049b3c4cafadc6d3d650c343fc","tid":2054132,"uid":309121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb0aa32c143aeaf95bb18e68efa4235db7aae450","tid":2054132,"uid":59953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T02:22:05.000Z","msg":"每隔兩三年就復發<br />\n好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n有冇人根治到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T03:07:10.000Z","msg":"我食咗5年藥，停藥十幾年了。當初教書太上心，對學生、對行政都瞓曬身。辛苦得嚟，同學生關係又緊張，而校方一味&ldquo;行政主導&rdquo;而輕視教育嘅初心。壓力爆錶，那時得病，不知有冇關係。後來調整心態，對行政工作做完就算反正都係上層要交數、佢哋要湊業績上位，有幾多真心為栽培學生？對學生就放低所謂嘅老師樽鹽，當佢哋係小師弟、小師妹。唔ㄧ定要佢哋聽聽話話，只强調可以錯，但一定要認，盡力去改。關係好好多，成績都有增值。自己有無乜壓力。"},{"pid":"4b5d577da7ff112d985888fcaa9d0fe8360ebee1","tid":2054132,"uid":287329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T03:19:32.000Z","msg":"發緊第二次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7a0e8f3c395e55e8d8f517ff5b0e5c80e0077d","tid":2054132,"uid":59953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b5d577da7ff112d985888fcaa9d0fe8360ebee1","tid":2054132,"uid":287329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"